{"tid":805214,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣倒追男網友","createTime":"2018-09-03T15:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T17:44:59.000Z","uid":200587,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"73837f8e6d3bb674d548bb248805b4283ef2cf70","tid":805214,"uid":200587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n前幾日見另一個網友，同佢傾計幾舒服 (最初佢話我無乜點出聲，不過後來大家開始多野講) 我覺得佢係一個幾好嘅對象。不過問題黎啦：<br />\n<br />\n1. 佢對愛情抱住順其自然嘅心態，之前問佢都試過同異性朋友出來食飯(friend搭friend識)，不過後來做左朋友.....<br />\n<br />\n2. 雖然出到黎見大家都有傾有講，不過一去到whatsapp好似無乜火花。我每次whatsapp佢都會應一兩句，但係就好難延續唔到落去<br />\n<br />\n其實whatsapp呢啲野係咪唔使成日講？理想情況應該幾耐傾一次？一個月唔whatsapp又得唔得?<br />\n<br />\n求各位巴絲打俾意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa69c5b150124e26814c1f73cd407e2d827266b","tid":805214,"uid":21558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:13:50.000Z","msg":"見完面態度仲不冷不熱<br />\n不如你放棄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實男方態度好明顯"},{"pid":"b05ae61faf4dd019a320c2f2038545d40c7c2842","tid":805214,"uid":132227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9aa69c5b150124e26814c1f73cd407e2d827266b","tid":805214,"uid":21558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:13:50.000Z","msg":"見完面態度仲不冷不熱<br />\n不如你放棄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實男方態度好明顯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"有時係特登對你冷淡啲喎"},{"pid":"45892c0fdbafc46ce5bd73ecea5af5cbc22584f9","tid":805214,"uid":61903,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9aa69c5b150124e26814c1f73cd407e2d827266b","tid":805214,"uid":21558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201